24:17.790 --> 24:18.757 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Hello to both of you.

24:18.791 --> 24:19.925 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
TAMARA KEITH, National Public
Radio: Hello.

24:19.958 --> 24:21.694 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
AMY WALTER, The Cook Political
Report: Hello,
Judy.

24:21.727 --> 24:23.662 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: So, we just heard
from these
