24:25.998 --> 24:27.399 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
AMY WALTER: Yes, it is.

24:27.433 --> 24:29.068 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Why then is
Donald Trump continuing
to talk about it?

24:29.101 --> 24:30.903 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
AMY WALTER: It's pretty simple.

24:30.936 --> 24:34.440 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It's about trying to suppress
voters from
turning out, and specifically
people who would

24:34.473 --> 24:37.142 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
