turning out
and voting.

24:37.176 --> 24:41.280 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
If you're talking about going
into certain
neighborhoods and literally
standing there

24:41.313 --> 24:46.352 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
to watch people vote, that says
make sure
that those people don't come out
and vote.

24:46.385 --> 24:50.823 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Now, the danger of making saying
that the
election overall is rigged, vs.
they're trying

24:50.856 --> 24:55.694 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
