going to turn out badly anyway?

24:59.098 --> 25:00.999 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: So, what does
that mean, Tamara?

25:01.033 --> 25:07.072 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
TAMARA KEITH: Well, and he
really has shifted
into more broadly not just
talking about something

25:07.106 --> 25:08.874 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
