voters going to respond to that?

25:21.854 --> 25:23.922 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
And that is not clear.

25:23.956 --> 25:27.593 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
So, yes, we're in uncharted
territory.

25:27.626 --> 25:31.130 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: But it's
something that he
continues to write about, to
tweet about.

25:31.163 --> 25:37.436 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
All right, I want to turn you,
