getting more employees
overseas.

26:03.328 --> 26:04.763 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
TAMARA KEITH: Right.

26:04.797 --> 26:08.667 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
