who asked an official at the
State Department

26:33.025 --> 26:34.760 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
about something.

26:34.793 --> 26:39.364 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
So, it wasn't the State
Department that was
initiating the apparently
nonexistent quid

26:39.398 --> 26:41.300 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
pro quo.

26:41.333 --> 26:45.504 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But here's what really matters,
