that it's the FBI and e-mail and
Hillary Clinton

27:17.936 --> 27:19.638 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
in the headline.

27:19.671 --> 27:22.875 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It's also the sense that the
