specifically to answer

27:39.825 --> 27:42.694 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
some of the stuff she said in
private, but
hasn't said in public.

27:42.728 --> 27:46.832 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I thought her answer at the her
answer at
the last debate, this was sort
