27:46.865 --> 27:51.436 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I sort of imagine myself being
Abraham Lincoln,
fell really, really flat.

27:51.470 --> 27:56.942 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
If that's her answer to more
