28:17.729 --> 28:19.498 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
AMY WALTER: The movie "Lincoln,"
right.

28:19.531 --> 28:23.735 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Is her camp -- is
she prepared,
Tam, based on your reporting, to
talk about

28:23.769 --> 28:27.739 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
this some more, to give more of
an explanation
about what's going on?

28:27.773 --> 28:29.575 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
TAMARA KEITH: She is certainly
preparing.

28:29.608 --> 28:32.077 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
That's for sure, because she's
been off the
trail for several days.

28:32.110 --> 28:35.614 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
She's not going to be on the
trail today,
tomorrow.

28:35.647 --> 28:36.782 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
And then there is the debate.

28:36.815 --> 28:38.817 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Well, let's go
back to Donald
Trump.

28:38.850 --> 28:43.388 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
