talking.

29:01.340 --> 29:03.141 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Hear's what Melania Trump had to
say.

29:03.175 --> 29:07.079 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MELANIA TRUMP, Wife of Donald
Trump: I said
to my husband that, you know,
the language

29:07.112 --> 29:16.254 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
is inappropriate, it's not
acceptable, and
I was surprised, because that is
not the man

29:16.288 --> 29:17.623 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
that I know.

29:17.656 --> 29:23.028 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And, as you can see from the
tape, the cameras
were not on.

29:23.061 --> 29:25.697 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
It was only a mike.

29:25.731 --> 29:35.907 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And I wonder if they even knew
that the mike
was on, because it was kind of
boy talk, and

29:35.941 --> 29:46.918 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
he was led on, like egged on
from the host
to say dirty and bad stuff.

29:46.952 --> 29:51.423 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: So, Amy, this is
10 days after
that tape came out.

29:51.456 --> 29:55.327 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
It's after we have seen Donald
Trump losing
support among women voters.

29:55.360 --> 29:56.561 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Does this make...

29:56.595 --> 29:58.764 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
AMY WALTER: And now -- right,
they put his
wife out...

29:58.797 --> 30:00.265 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Right.

30:00.298 --> 30:02.300 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
AMY WALTER: ... which she can
help to sort
of soften the edge on this.

30:02.334 --> 30:08.907 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But her answer and her -- the
way she is defending
her husband is not much
different from what

30:08.940 --> 30:11.443 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
