this was
locker room talk.

30:11.476 --> 30:16.348 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But when you look at the polling
that has
been taking place since this
locker room talk

30:16.381 --> 30:17.849 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
came out, you're right.

30:17.883 --> 30:19.217 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
He lost support in the polls.

30:19.251 --> 30:21.086 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
He's losing support among women.

30:21.119 --> 30:25.691 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
