expanding
the battleground now.

31:05.397 --> 31:07.099 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
TAMARA KEITH: They're expanding
the map.

31:07.132 --> 31:10.702 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
Bernie Sanders will be
campaigning in Arizona,
Arizona, tomorrow.

31:10.736 --> 31:16.975 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
