spend about $2
million.

31:21.079 --> 31:24.349 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
It's basically a tossup now and
they think
it's a possible pickup.

31:24.382 --> 31:29.654 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And there's the added benefit of
making your
opponent have to compete in a
state where

31:29.688 --> 31:31.590 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
