32:42.627 --> 32:49.701 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: But first: As
Europe continues
to struggle with the refugee
crisis, Denmark's

32:49.734 --> 32:55.040 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
