electorate
is moving to the right.

33:01.880 --> 33:07.586 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
After complaints, people have
filed charges
of racism against an extreme
right-wing party

33:07.619 --> 33:11.389 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
which has been handing out what
it calls asylum
sprays.

33:11.423 --> 33:16.161 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
From Thisted in Northwest
Denmark, Malcolm
Brabant reports.

33:16.194 --> 33:23.168 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MALCOLM BRABANT: In a small town
250 miles
from cosmopolitan Copenhagen,
the new Party

33:23.201 --> 33:28.673 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
of the Danes is distributing
what it calls
asylum spray, ostensibly as a
defense against

33:28.707 --> 33:32.077 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
potential immigrant sex
attackers.

33:32.110 --> 33:35.547 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The campaign has been condemned
as provocative
and xenophobic.

33:35.580 --> 33:38.617 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Nonetheless, the spray finds
several takers.

33:38.650 --> 33:42.420 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WOMAN (through translator): It's
my daughter
that needs it, the way Danish
society is at

33:42.454 --> 33:44.155 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
the moment.

33:44.189 --> 33:47.058 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WOMAN (through translator): They
can't just
come here and do whatever they
want, like

33:47.092 --> 33:49.494 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
