and stuff.

33:49.527 --> 33:51.630 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
They shouldn't be allowed do
that.

33:51.663 --> 33:56.301 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MALCOLM BRABANT: The spray was
conceived by
party leader Daniel Carlsen, who
admits denying

33:56.334 --> 34:00.939 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
