is now trying
to win support to run for
Parliament.

34:00.972 --> 34:08.680 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MAN: I think we have too many
people in Denmark
from Arab countries.

34:08.713 --> 34:10.181 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
I don't like it.

34:10.215 --> 34:12.017 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
I don't like Muslims.

34:12.050 --> 34:16.087 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MALCOLM BRABANT: This region of
Denmark is
fertile ground for the right.

34:16.121 --> 34:20.926 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And even though the cans only
contain hair
spray, the symbolism touches a
chord.

34:20.959 --> 34:24.829 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WOMAN (through translator): You
never know
what can happen.

34:24.863 --> 34:27.499 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Just a month ago, I was followed
home on my
bike.

34:27.532 --> 34:31.636 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MALCOLM BRABANT: Organizations
like the United
Nations High Commissioner for
Refugees think

34:31.670 --> 34:32.637 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
what you're doing is disgusting.

34:32.671 --> 34:34.439 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
What's your response?

34:34.472 --> 34:37.609 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DANIEL CARLSEN, Leader, Party of
the Danes:
They are working for and
promoting an invasion

34:37.642 --> 34:44.215 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
to Europe, an invasion that, by
time, will
replace the indigenous Europeans
here with

34:44.249 --> 34:46.985 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
people from the non-Western
world.

34:47.018 --> 34:48.920 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
I think that is disgusting.

34:48.954 --> 34:53.525 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And what their politics are
resulting in,
we see that in Europe every day
now.

34:53.558 --> 34:56.861 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
We see rapes, like the incidents
in Cologne.

34:56.895 --> 35:03.101 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
