entertaining schoolchildren
and educating them about the war
in Syria.

35:46.311 --> 35:49.581 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Music has opened doors that are
closed to
other refugees.

35:49.614 --> 35:56.521 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
NOUR AMORA (through translator):
I tell my
friends that now it is not good
to come to

35:56.554 --> 36:00.759 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
Denmark because of the
government, but if
you do come, you will find that
the Danish

36:00.792 --> 36:03.728 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
people are really nice.

36:03.762 --> 36:11.102 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MALCOLM BRABANT: Singer Leila
Rong Hanna was
born in Denmark.

36:11.136 --> 36:15.440 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
She has Syrian and Norwegian
heritage, but
has dissuaded relatives in
Damascus and the

36:15.473 --> 36:18.176 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
