China for
belonging to Falun Gong, the
outlawed spiritual

38:34.279 --> 38:36.080 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
movement.

38:36.114 --> 38:39.350 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CHEN MAN, Chinese Asylum Seeker:
I feel, like,
worried, because I feel, like,
unstable for

38:39.384 --> 38:40.351 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
my security.

38:40.385 --> 38:43.054 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
I need a kind of protection from
the nation.

38:43.087 --> 38:48.860 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But if I cannot have, the risk
of myself is
going back to China and facing
the imprisonment

38:48.893 --> 38:50.662 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
again.

38:50.695 --> 38:53.798 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MALCOLM BRABANT: Chen Man
believes Denmark's
hostility towards asylum seekers
is a sign

38:53.831 --> 38:55.066 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
of weakness.

38:55.099 --> 38:58.136 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
CHEN MAN: Yes, this is not the
way to resolve
the problem.

38:58.169 --> 39:03.441 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And it's also a kind of way to
show the fear
inside, because if you are
strong enough,

39:03.474 --> 39:08.279 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
you can handle that without
building up a
wall, but a bridge.

39:08.313 --> 39:11.583 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MALCOLM BRABANT: So what's the
source of Denmark's
right turn?

39:11.616 --> 39:14.552 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Is it from the population or
political ideology?

39:14.586 --> 39:18.556 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Nils Holtug is the director of
migration studies
at Copenhagen University.

39:18.590 --> 39:22.727 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
NILS HOLTUG, Copenhagen
University: I think,
to some extent, politicians have
probably

39:22.760 --> 39:27.899 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
been responding to what are real
worries amongst
Danes.

39:27.932 --> 39:35.373 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But they have also been driving
those worries,
so -- especially the Danish
People's Party,

39:35.406 --> 39:39.043 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
but also some of the new parties
that are
coming up now.

39:39.077 --> 39:43.181 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
I think the Dane Party is very
worrying.

39:43.214 --> 39:50.188 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And it was established by former
members of
a Nazi movement in Denmark.

39:50.221 --> 39:52.957 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
So I'm actually quite worried
about that.

39:52.991 --> 39:54.025 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
MALCOLM BRABANT: Are you a Nazi?

39:54.058 --> 39:55.260 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
DANIEL CARLSEN: No.

39:55.293 --> 39:56.894 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MALCOLM BRABANT: But you were a
National Socialist
before?

39:56.928 --> 39:58.129 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
DANIEL CARLSEN: I'm a National
Democrat.

39:58.162 --> 40:00.131 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MALCOLM BRABANT: But you were a
National Socialist
before.

40:00.164 --> 40:01.666 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
DANIEL CARLSEN: Before.

40:01.699 --> 40:04.102 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MALCOLM BRABANT: So, are you
saying you're
a reformed National Socialist?

40:04.135 --> 40:05.970 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
DANIEL CARLSEN: No, I'm a
National Democrat.

40:06.004 --> 40:09.774 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MALCOLM BRABANT: But you were a
National Socialist
-- and that was the Nazi Party
-- before.

40:09.807 --> 40:14.078 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
What's happening in Denmark is
consistent
with a surge to the right across
Europe.

40:14.112 --> 40:19.584 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
One of the more controversial
pieces of legislation
enacted here was the so-called
jewelry law,

40:19.617 --> 40:26.224 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
which authorized the authorities
to confiscate
the assets of those migrants and
refugees

40:26.257 --> 40:30.528 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
deemed wealthy enough to be able
to pay for
themselves, rather than relying
on the state.

40:30.561 --> 40:36.134 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Now, that law came into effect
in February,
and it's only been used three
times.

40:36.167 --> 40:40.972 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Now, the Danish government may
have attracted
lots of international criticism
for its methods,

40:41.005 --> 40:46.611 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
but ministers say that there are
other European
countries that are seeking their
advice about

40:46.644 --> 40:50.615 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
how to reduce their numbers.

40:50.648 --> 40:54.819 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
With Syria still spinning out of
control and
Europe's migration crisis
showing no sign

40:54.852 --> 40:59.724 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
of abating, does Denmark feel
the need to
toughen its stance still
further, a question

40:59.757 --> 41:02.060 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
for the government's migration
spokesman,
Marcus Knuth.

41:02.093 --> 41:06.831 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MARCUS KNUTH, Liberal Party:
Part of the reason
why we have such a low influx of
asylum seekers

41:06.864 --> 41:10.468 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
right now is also because of the
E.U. deal
with Turkey.

41:10.501 --> 41:15.306 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
If that deal breaks, if there's
more trouble
in the Middle East and so forth,
everything

41:15.340 --> 41:16.808 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
can change.

41:16.841 --> 41:20.011 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So, right now, we're happy that
the situation
seems to be under control.

41:20.044 --> 41:23.848 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But there are so many factors
out there that
things can change.

41:23.881 --> 41:28.519 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MALCOLM BRABANT: A strong police
presence
forces refugee supporters to
keep their distance

41:28.553 --> 41:33.324 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
from a monthly anti-Muslim
demonstration.

41:33.358 --> 41:38.229 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
They demand asylum for all,
while the right-wingers
deplore the growth of Islam.

41:38.262 --> 41:41.632 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
The migration crisis is
polarizing European
society.

41:41.666 --> 41:46.504 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Although the numbers prepared to
demonstrate
on the streets aren't great,
opinion polls

41:46.537 --> 41:52.043 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
show sentiments expressed at
gatherings like
this are gaining traction, not
just in Denmark,

41:52.076 --> 41:53.478 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
but across the continent.

41:53.511 --> 41:59.717 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
For the "PBS NewsHour," I'm
Malcolm Brabant
in Copenhagen.

41:59.751 --> 42:12.096 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: With the U.S.
health care system
undergoing its biggest changes
in decades,

42:12.130 --> 42:18.269 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
health experts are looking to an
unexpected
place, sub-Saharan Africa, for
inspiration.

42:18.302 --> 42:22.673 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Throughout the continent,
ordinary citizens
are routinely trained as
community health

42:22.707 --> 42:24.475 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
workers.

42:24.509 --> 42:28.980 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
As Sarah Varney reports on the
lessons to
learn, this story was produced
in collaboration

42:29.013 --> 42:31.649 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
with our partner Kaiser Health
News.

42:31.682 --> 42:37.355 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SARAH VARNEY: Destini Belton is
on a mission
to improve health outcomes in
Harlem.

42:37.388 --> 42:41.893 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
She's not a doctor or a nurse,
but she knows
this neighborhood and the people
who live

42:41.926 --> 42:43.761 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
here.

42:43.795 --> 42:48.499 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Belton goes where clinics and
hospitals can't,
into patients' homes, to
understand the mundane,

42:48.533 --> 42:50.501 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
but vital details of their
lives.

42:50.535 --> 42:51.536 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
DESTINI BELTON, Community Health
Worker: Hi.

42:51.569 --> 42:52.537 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
How are you?

42:52.570 --> 42:55.239 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Oh, your hair looks nice now.

42:55.273 --> 42:56.374 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
How are you feeling?

42:56.407 --> 42:58.142 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JESSICA GONZALEZ, Diabetes
Sufferer: OK.

42:58.176 --> 43:01.412 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SARAH VARNEY: She visits people
like Jessica
Gonzalez, who was blinded by
uncontrolled

43:01.446 --> 43:03.448 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
type one diabetes at age 22.

43:03.481 --> 43:05.349 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
DESTINI BELTON: Let me take your
blood pressure.

43:05.383 --> 43:11.055 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SARAH VARNEY: Now 33, Gonzalez
has high blood
pressure, high cholesterol and
renal disease,

43:11.088 --> 43:15.092 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
and Belton worries that she has
trouble keeping
her medications straight because
she can't

43:15.126 --> 43:16.494 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
see them.

43:16.527 --> 43:18.629 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
DESTINI BELTON: You take most of
them during
what time of the day?

43:18.663 --> 43:20.298 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JESSICA GONZALEZ: During the day
or after
breakfast.

43:20.331 --> 43:22.099 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
DESTINI BELTON: During the day.

43:22.133 --> 43:25.736 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SARAH VARNEY: Gonzalez is
reluctant to admit
her struggles to her doctor, but
she trusts

43:25.770 --> 43:27.605 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Belton to understand.

43:27.638 --> 43:31.275 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JESSICA GONZALEZ: With your
doctor, you don't
really want to say what you eat,
so I'm able

43:31.309 --> 43:37.248 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
to tell her like, really, if I'm
not going
well, or, you know, if I sneaked
and cheated.

43:37.281 --> 43:39.717 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I tell her the right things, and
she helps
me.

43:39.750 --> 43:45.389 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MANMEET KAUR, City Health Works:
East Harlem
in particular has the highest
rate of diet-related

43:45.423 --> 43:47.191 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
diseases in New York.

43:47.225 --> 43:50.895 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SARAH VARNEY: Manmeet Kaur has
trained a small
team of these community health
workers in

43:50.928 --> 43:52.597 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
New York City.

43:52.630 --> 43:55.199 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MANMEET KAUR: East Harlem in
particular has
the highest rate of diet-related
diseases

43:55.233 --> 43:56.968 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
in New York.

43:57.001 --> 44:00.638 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SARAH VARNEY: The organization,
called City
Health Works, contracts with
primary care

44:00.671 --> 44:05.076 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
providers, like Mount Sinai
Health System,
to better manage their most
difficult patients.

44:05.109 --> 44:08.880 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WOMAN: Today, we're going to be
doing a workshop
on healthy beverages.

44:08.913 --> 44:13.518 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SARAH VARNEY: Nearly all of
their clients
are poor and facing chronic
illnesses that

44:13.551 --> 44:15.753 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
frequently spiral out of
control.

44:15.786 --> 44:21.158 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
They work to stabilize their
health and avoid
costly visits to the emergency
room and lengthy

44:21.192 --> 44:23.895 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
hospital stays.

44:23.928 --> 44:30.568 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Employing community health
workers is a common
strategy elsewhere in the world.

44:30.601 --> 44:36.007 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
In sub-Saharan Africa, community
health workers
have long formed the backbone of
health systems,

44:36.040 --> 44:40.144 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
filling in gaps where doctors
and nurses are
in short supply.

44:40.177 --> 44:45.483 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It was Thandi Blie in Cape Town,
South Africa,
in fact, who helped to inspire
Kaur to start

44:45.516 --> 44:46.517 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
City Health Works.

44:46.551 --> 44:49.253 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
THANDI BLIE, Mamelani Projects:
Hi.

44:49.287 --> 44:50.254 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
Hello.

44:50.288 --> 44:52.023 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
WOMAN: How are you?

44:52.056 --> 44:54.225 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
THANDI BLIE: I'm fine.

44:54.258 --> 44:55.226 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Thank you.

44:55.259 --> 44:56.227 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
And how are you, my dear?

44:56.260 --> 44:57.228 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
WOMAN: I'm good.

44:57.261 --> 44:59.063 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
THANDI BLIE: Long time no see.

44:59.096 --> 45:03.668 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SARAH VARNEY: They met when Kaur
worked with
a group called Mamelani
Projects, a nonprofit

45:03.701 --> 45:08.539 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
that relies on regular women
like Blie to
help neighbors improve their
health habits.

45:08.573 --> 45:16.080 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
THANDI BLIE: I remember, last
time, when we
met, you had issues or problems
about your

45:16.113 --> 45:17.214 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
high blood problem.

45:17.248 --> 45:19.317 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
SARAH VARNEY: Often by sharing
their own experience.

45:19.350 --> 45:22.620 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
THANDI BLIE: Yes, because really
high blood
pressure is very dangerous.

45:22.653 --> 45:24.322 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
I know it from me.

45:24.355 --> 45:29.160 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SARAH VARNEY: She often shares
how her once
high blood pressure led to a
stroke.

45:29.193 --> 45:33.598 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
THANDI BLIE: I make the examples
about what
happens in me.

45:33.631 --> 45:38.669 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Then, as soon as I share maybe a
story, someone
say, and me too.

45:38.703 --> 45:44.041 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SARAH VARNEY: Long lines besiege
clinics and
hospitals in South Africa, where
apartheid-era

45:44.075 --> 45:49.547 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
laws have left a legacy of
widespread poverty
and desperate health conditions.

45:49.580 --> 45:53.951 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Mamelani's health coaches say
that, just as
in New York City, those
realities are often

45:53.985 --> 46:01.759 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
best confronted outside the
walls of medical
clinics by bringing health
education to areas

46:01.792 --> 46:03.894 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
that need it most.

46:03.928 --> 46:07.965 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The women who've attended these
classes are
making lasting changes to their
own health

46:07.999 --> 46:10.901 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
and in the wider community.

46:10.935 --> 46:15.640 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Mickey Linda used her own
pension to start
a soup kitchen after hearing
that neighbors

46:15.673 --> 46:20.845 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
were taking powerful drugs to
treat HIV on
empty stomachs.

46:20.878 --> 46:25.483 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
With nutrition training from
Mamelani, she
now cooks up healthier meals for
hundreds

46:25.516 --> 46:30.287 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
of neighbors and serves as a
vital local health
resource, keeping watch over her
community.

46:30.321 --> 46:33.324 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MICKEY LINDA, Started Soup
Kitchen: Because
doctors are not staying here.

46:33.357 --> 46:35.159 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Doctors are staying in town.

46:35.192 --> 46:42.566 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It's us who see that we can talk
about health
to them, because we are staying
together here.

46:42.600 --> 46:47.171 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
It's us who see them, that this
is this problem
this problem.

46:47.204 --> 46:53.277 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SARAH VARNEY: Those close social
ties undergird
much of life in South Africa,
says Mamelani's

46:53.310 --> 46:56.814 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
founder, Carly Tanur.

46:56.847 --> 47:01.218 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
She and her team are working
closely with
Manmeet Kaur back in Harlem to
figure out

47:01.252 --> 47:05.890 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
how Mamelani's model could be
incorporated
more broadly into the U.S.
health care system.

47:05.923 --> 47:11.195 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But here in Harlem, the question
is, how can
this model fit into a sprawling
hospital system

47:11.228 --> 47:15.566 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
like Mount Sinai, especially at
a time when
health care leaders are
searching for ways

47:15.599 --> 47:19.336 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
to control the cost of caring
for chronically
ill patients?

